Awards

Notable examples of awards received by the Lexus LS include World Car of the Year (WCOTY),251 International Car of the Year (ICOTY),252 Japan Car of the Year (JCOTY),253 Canadian Car of the Year,254 Wheels Car of the Year,255 and Top Gear Limousine of the Year.256 The Lexus LS has been the highest-rated luxury car in Automobile Magazine,257 Car and Driver,258259 Consumer Reports,260261 Fleet World,262 and MotorWeek.263 In J.D. Power's long-term Vehicle Dependability Study, the Lexus LS has been the most reliable car for fifteen consecutive years,264265266 the most for any manufacturer,267268269 and Consumer Reports has ranked the sedan as the most reliable vehicle tested.270271272273 Safety awards include Auto Bild's 2007 Innovation Prize for the LS 460 pre-collision system,274 consecutive first place rankings in the What Car? Security Supertest,275276 and Kiplinger's &quot;Best in Safety for Cars $40,000 and Over&quot;.277 Technical honors range from Ward's 10 Best Engines,278279 to Edmunds.com's &quot;Best Sound System in Cars Over $30,000&quot;,280 and the Society of Automotive Engineers (SAE) 2007 &quot;Best Engineered Vehicle&quot; award.281
